Data.name: CtrlTestsInTestPlanAllButPASS FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE', 'TODO|EXECUTING|FAIL|ABORTED|BLOCKED') ORDER BY rank

Data.name: CtrlTestsInTestPlanAllTODO FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE', TODO) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: CtrlTestsInTestPlanAllTODOUnassigned FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE', TODO, __NULL__) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: CtrlTestsInTestPlanFAIL FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE', FAIL) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlan FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE') ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanOpen FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE') AND status not in (Closed, Resolved) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanOpenCritical FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE') AND status not in (Closed, Resolved) AND Priority = critical ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanOpenFlagged FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE') AND status not in (Closed, Resolved) AND flagged is not EMPTY ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanOpenInTreatment FNC BE
Data.description: Defects in treatment by MPT for BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE') AND status not in (Closed, Resolved) AND assignee in (qtd2005, qtd0593, qt76380, qtc6712, qtb4864, qxz084o, qxz0c91) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanOpenMPT FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE') AND status not in (Closed, Resolved) AND labels not in (Sofico) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanOpenReTest FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE') AND status not in (Closed, Resolved) AND assignee not in (qtd2005, qtd0593, qt76380, qtc6712, qtb4864, qxz084o, qxz0c91) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanOpenSofico FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE') AND status not in (Closed, Resolved) AND labels in (Sofico) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTTestExecsInTestPlan FNC BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testPlanTestExecutions(MILES4ALL-8345) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTTestExecsInTestPlanAssignedToCurrentUser FNC BE
Data.description: Executions in Test Plan for current user
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND  filter=270731 AND issue in testExecWithTestRunsAssignedToUser() ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTTestsInTestPlan FNC BE
